<emphasis box="[565,605,834,858]" italics="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="2970">m).</emphasis>
Body length 1900. Head, length 172; median width 132; postocular setae 42. Pronotum, length 155; width 175; major setae am 3, aa 30, ml 3, epim 44, pa 42. Tergite IX setae S1 68, S2 102, S3 80. Tube length 100; basal width 60; anal setae 152. Antennal segments III–VIII length 32, 40, 34, 36, 36, 26.
</paragraph>
